      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_10_57944-58105",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "57944-58105",
      "markText": "齐、晋、秦、楚兴起后，彼此保持着均势，相互间的边界变动也不大，它们的疆域扩展基本是靠“内取诸夏”和“外攘夷狄”来实现的，即兼并中原弱小诸侯和周边少数民族的土地，降服中原各邦是诸强的首选作战任务，它们制订的种种战略也受到上述地理形势的制约影响，多数内容围绕着以下目的——尽力去占领、控制中原地带，将对手驱除或阻隔于中原之外。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=57944&rangeEnd=58105",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=57944&rangeEnd=58105"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_11_16807-16850",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "16807-16850",
      "markText": "公元前564年，晋国会合齐、鲁、宋、卫等诸侯联军伐郑，楚军未能及时救援，郑国被迫求和。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=16807&rangeEnd=16850",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=16807&rangeEnd=16850"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_6_7532-7568",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7532-7568",
      "markText": "位于东亚大陆的南部，包括长江中下游、淮河、汉水及珠江流域。",
      "totalCount": 139,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7532&rangeEnd=7568",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7532&rangeEnd=7568"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_7_15540-15663",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "15540-15663",
      "markText": "而关中平原大部分还处在游牧民族的控制下，虽有个别农耕民族在那里活动，也不免“窜于戎狄之间”。",
      "totalCount": 139,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15540&rangeEnd=15663",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15540&rangeEnd=15663"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_7_9467-9501",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "9467-9501",
      "markText": "汤伐桀的作战经过，《诗·商颂·长发》曰：“韦、顾既伐，昆吾、夏桀。”",
      "totalCount": 138,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9467&rangeEnd=9501",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9467&rangeEnd=9501"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_6_13259-13617",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13259-13617",
      "markText": "如夏族原居河东，禹曾在安邑、平阳等地设都，为了适应和东夷、有苗作战的需要，他迁都到黄河以南、临近东方的阳城、阳翟。",
      "totalCount": 137,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13259&rangeEnd=13617",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13259&rangeEnd=13617"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_7_2981-3010",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2981-3010",
      "markText": "《禹誓》曰：“大战于甘，王乃命左右六人，下，听誓于中军。”",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2981&rangeEnd=3010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2981&rangeEnd=3010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300153951_13_12228-12261",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "12228-12261",
      "markText": "魏都安邑处在几条道路交汇的中心，北过绛、平阳、晋阳，即可直达代北。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12228&rangeEnd=12261",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=12228&rangeEnd=12261"
    },
    {
