      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "15486-15540",
      "markText": "夏朝到商初，西方主要民族夏族居住生活的基本区域是在豫西的伊洛平原、嵩山附近及南阳盆地，其次为晋南的“夏墟”。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300153951&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15486&rangeEnd=15540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c3b32180813aba2a3g0118dc?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15486&rangeEnd=15540"
    },
    {
